<td>≥ 80%</td>
<td>Cooper, Heron &amp; Heward (2020)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Sesi Berturut-turut</td>
<td>3</td>
<td>Mastery learning criterion</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Latihan per Sesi</td>
<td>5</td>
<td>Task Analysis Bab III</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
